OL,3,C'Urgent bail-out' needed to sort PSNI
OL,4,Cfunding 'crisis'
OL,6,FThe Police Federation for Northern
OL,7,FIreland says they need an "urgent-bail
OL,8,Fout" to sort out PSNI funding "crisis".
OL,10,FPFNI Chair Liam Kelly urged Secretary
OL,11,Fof State Hilary Benn to find a stable
OL,12,Fsolution for police funding, calling
OL,13,Fthe current process a "dangerous and
OL,14,Funbecoming game of musical chairs."
OL,16,FThe PSNI says it needs hundreds of
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds to cover major
OL,18,Fcosts, including compensation for the
OL,19,F2023 data breach and outstanding
OL,20,Fofficer holiday pay.
