OL,6,FAlongside this, there is no money
OL,7,Favailable to support the proposed
OL,8,FChief Constable's Recovery Plan, which
OL,9,Fneeds over #200 million in funding to
OL,10,Fincrease officer recruitment.
OL,12,FToday a Northern Ireland spokesperson
OL,13,Ftold UTV that "policing in Northern
OL,14,FIreland is largely a matter for the NI
OL,15,FExecutive."
OL,17,F'It's breaking them to the extent
OL,18,Fthey're unable to continue on in their
OL,19,Fpolicing careers'
