OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV Liam Kelly said: "Day-
OL,7,Fto-day operational in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fis indeed the Stormont Executive.
OL,10,F"However, there is security funding on
OL,11,Ftheir national security issues which
OL,12,Fis solely funded by UK government.
OL,14,F"My pushback to the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fand UK government is, if you have an
OL,16,Funder-resourced, under-pressure
OL,17,Fpolicing service, that has to have a
OL,18,Fdetrimental impact on our ability to
OL,19,Frespond and assist with national
OL,20,Fsecurity matters.
