OL,6,FWhat is the PSNI's funding model?
OL,8,FThe DoJ were allocated an additional
OL,9,F#6.7 million last week, to help fund
OL,10,Fpolice and prison officers pay
OL,11,Frewards. Kelly acknowledged this in
OL,12,Fhis statement, yet described it as a
OL,13,F"small expenditure item in the grand
OL,14,Fscheme of things".
OL,16,FPolicing Board members agreed today
OL,17,Fthat this should not all be a Stormont
OL,18,Fproblem, given that some of the costs
OL,19,Fwere not foreseen.
