OL,6,FIn a statement PFNI Chair Liam Kelly
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a funding perfect
OL,8,Fstorm. There is no money for the Chief
OL,9,FConstable's Recovery Plan. Happily, it
OL,10,Fseems police pay is likely to be
OL,11,Fresolved in Stormont's Monitoring
OL,12,FRound next month ` one less but
OL,13,Frelatively small expenditure item in
OL,14,Fthe grand scheme of things.
OL,16,F"There's a #23 million deficit to be
OL,17,Faddressed by Ministers before anything
OL,18,Felse can happen. That will have to be
OL,19,Fdealt with as a priority in the
OL,20,FMonitoring Round.
